page.title: 07Helen's Day Cont.
page.content:
At l2 o'clock it is dinner time. After dinner we have aqua pack (swimming lesson). It lasts till quarter past two then at 2.3O we have a break. After break we have games, rounders or football. At 3.3O the bell goes and we go home.
I have my tea at 5.45 then go to my friends for{Brownies.}The Brownies uniform is brown and a yellow tie. Brownies start at 6.3Opm tilll 8.OOpm. Sometimes we play games, sing and sometimes we gain badges. I go home at 8.OO o'clock.
On an evening I may go to play with my friends on their computers or play on our bikes before going to bed between 9.OOpm and 9.3Opm.
